<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
        .code {
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 24px;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #f4f4f4;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Reset Your Password</h2>
    <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
    <p>You recently requested to reset your password for your <%= appName %> account. Use the button below to reset it:</p>
    
    <p>
        <a href="<%= resetUrl %>" class="button">Reset Password</a>
    </p>
    
    <p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
    <p><%= resetUrl %></p>
    
    <p>This password reset link will expire in <%= expiresIn %>.</p>
    
    <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact support if you have questions.</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
